scoringPlays.text: Jerrod Heard 37 Yd pass from Shane Buechele (Trent Domingue Kick)
Devin Duvernay 75 Yd pass from Shane Buechele (Trent Domingue Kick)
D'Onta Foreman 18 Yd Run (Trent Domingue Kick)

videos.description: Shane Buechele avoids the blitz and finds Jerrod Heard wide open for 37 yd TD
videos.headline: Longhorns take first lead with long TD pass

videos.description: Mike Warren is stacked up at the line as Iowa State fails on 4th down at the Texas 25
videos.headline: Texas defense stands strong on 4th down stop

videos.description: Shane Buechele finds Devin Duvernay who races into the end zone for a 75-yard touchdown to put Texas up 17-6.
videos.headline: Duvernay unstoppable on 75-yard TD pass

videos.description: D'Onta Foreman goes untouched up the middle for 18 yd TD run to put Texas ahead 24-6
videos.headline: Longhorns starting to run away from Cyclones
